               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was walking along, and felt the handkerchief thrown against my feet—I picked it up—the prosecutor came, and said I had taken his handkerchief—I denied it, and walked away—he called "Stop thief," and I walked a little further.</p>
